# PATCH: 0026-inventory-extra-schedule
# WHY: Mở rộng inventory: thu thập thêm services + scheduled tasks + patch level (hotfixes + os_build);
#      và tự thu thập ĐỊNH KỲ (mặc định 4h/lần) cho mọi máy managed.
# WHAT: collect-inventory.ps1 +services (Win32_Service) +tasks (Get-ScheduledTask) +hotfixes
#       (Get-HotFix) +os_build. quickwin_winrs_inventory.go: config +collect_interval_min (default 240)
#       + LastCollect; collectHostInventory (helper); RunDueInventoryCollect (scheduler). root.go goroutine
#       5' gọi. UI: field interval + hiển thị services/tasks/hotfixes/os_build.
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0026-inventory-extra-schedule.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
